      <section eId="sec_122">
        <num>122</num>
        <heading>Local laws or ordinances</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_122__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>impose penalties for violation of such restrictions to be\nrecovered in a civil action in the name of such municipality;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_122__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>provide for enforcement by fine or imprisonment for any such\nviolation; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_122__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>provide for the issuance pursuant to the criminal procedure law of\nan appearance ticket, or in lieu thereof, a uniform appearance ticket,\nor in lieu thereof, a uniform appearance ticket and simplified\ninformation, as provided in section one hundred thirteen of this\narticle, by any dog control officer, peace officer, acting pursuant to\nhis special duties, or police officer, who is authorized by any\nmunicipality to assist in the enforcement of this article for any such\nviolation.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
